ğŸ’¡ Notes
Ensure car_purchase_data.csv is in the same directory as the script.
The model uses 80% training data and 20% testing data.
The K-value (neighbors) is set to 5 using the Euclidean distance metric (p=2).
The confusion matrix evaluates the performance of the model.
